{"tid":947772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【本土研究社】政府低估棕地潛力","createTime":"2018-12-19T13:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-20T03:36:12.000Z","uid":138409,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2250b3d8ea8881b455c10b312b0f14c8915551fa","tid":947772,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434028-20181219.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434028-20181219.htm&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=e54d453b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1434028-20181219.htm&h=54e686cd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1434028-20181219.htm</a><br />\n本土研究社發現，去年新界棕土總面積為1521公頃，較政府及土地供應專責小組指的1300公頃，<span style=\"color: red;\">多出200多公頃</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他們發表研究報告，指<span style=\"color: red;\">約有1023公頃棕土未納入各新發展區及210幅具房屋發展潛力用地範圍內</span>，質疑政府貶低棕土的潛力。<br />\n<br />\n報告指出，去年涉及露天重型作業的棕土面積約63公頃，佔新界棕土的總面積約百分之4。研究社質疑，<span style=\"color: red;\">棕土作業的重置難度被誇大</span>。<br />\n<br />\n研究發現，<span style=\"color: red;\">由1993年至去年，棕土總面積大幅增長近一倍</span>。根據相關衛星圖，發現約有433公頃屬非重型的露天作業棕土，連同有蓋倉庫或工場及露天停車場等，約有1206公頃為適合遷進多層大廈的棕土作業。<br />\n<br />\n研究社批評，政府未有提供全面棕土數據，亦未展開普查下已進行公眾諮詢，認為諮詢結果不能作為真實民意反映及發展理據。"},{"pid":"cfdafe08c075b57c2930cd99ab528e6d3895ebe5","tid":947772,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T13:40:54.000Z","msg":"報告全文<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC%2Fview&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6c62b15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC/view</a><br />\n<br />\n還明日新界一個未來，請即支持棕土研究計劃：<a href=