%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%9C%AA%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%94760%E5%85%AC%E9%A0%83-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%94%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9A%9F%E8%B5%B7%E6%A8%93\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F188010%2F%25E5%259C%2596%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%259C%259F%25E5%259C%25B0%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%259C%25AA%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%2599%25BC%25E6%25A3%2595%25E5%259C%25B0%25E9%2581%2594760%25E5%2585%25AC%25E9%25A0%2583-%25E9%25BB%259E%25E8%25A7%25A3%25E5%2594%2594%25E7%2594%25A8%25E5%259A%259F%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E6%25A8%2593&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=52692e42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/188010/%E5%9C%96%E8%A7%A3%E5%9C%9F%E5%9C%B0%E5%A4%A7%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%9C%AA%E9%96%8B%E7%99%BC%E6%A3%95%E5%9C%B0%E9%81%94760%E5%85%AC%E9%A0%83-%E9%BB%9E%E8%A7%A3%E5%94%94%E7%94%A8%E5%9A%9F%E8%B5%B7%E6%A8%93</a><br />\n冇人耕田,唔代表就咁趕走佢地就得架<br />\n而家黑社會??<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"警察托㗎？<br />\n打示威者就咁勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n至於篇文裡面提到嘅問題<br />\n基本上本土研究社已經反駁咗<br />\n首先棕地並不零散<br />\n//研究團隊發現相連的棕土群達1 172公頃,主要分佈在新界西(洪水橋、元朗南、八鄉和龍鼓灘一帶),然而,現時未被納入發展區內的棕土達723公頃。<br />\n2. 這些大量的相鄰棕土群面積每個至少2公頃,並非零碎,其發展潛力應被研究, 例如發展低密度鄉村式公屋。<br />\n3. 以面積計,首20大的相鄰棕土群總面積達790公頃,然而將近一半(391公頃) 並未放入發展計劃中或沒有發展時間表,這些棕土被政府及土供組完全忽略。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WpiXvM_k_6MtQAgQ6uSTkQgWgHd4-OJ9/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1WpiXvM_k_6MtQAgQ6uSTkQgWgHd4-OJ9%2Fview&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=64f2eaea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WpiXvM_k_6MtQAgQ6uSTkQgWgHd4-OJ9/view</a><br />\n<br />\n另外今次報告其中一個發現<br />\n係重型作業佔棕地嘅面積僅4%左右<br />\n其他作業都係可以搬去多層作業大廈<br />\n<br />\n//土地供應潛力:2017 年的棕土當中,有 1,023 公頃未納入各新發展區範圍及政府公佈的「210 多幅具房屋發展潛力用地」。這些棕土若透過適當的重置及環境修復措施,可被視為潛在土地供應來源。而較難遷入多層工廈的露天重型作業類棕土只有 63 公頃,(佔 2017 年棕土總數的 4.1%),預計對重置棕土所帶來的土地需求壓力不大。//<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC%2Fview&d=CHFhjoo8w1HKizAhJiV8rE%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=6c62b15e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UdM-BuFxHGikkzlDJHZPglG86MvW6_cC/view</a>"},{"pid":"8ae17fbbbb52c31130b120ec26388dd8b6c14e8d","tid":947772,"uid":138409,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"369df5cd07651b7178c3f84ae68e756b005797c3","tid":947772,"uid":97389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9c289035e9c9138c57b9839ee500e9c964b0eb67","tid":947772,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969c6bf5fb64ce8ebbcdc25f223d1adc8876b2c4","tid":947772,"uid":97389,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T14:32:17.000Z","msg":"正確D來講, 係寧願倒1兆落海都唔俾新界佬賺1毫子的非理性/經濟原則考慮的決定?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n政府, 只有D咁極端的想法先唔考慮收棕地呢個方案, 定係拋填海方案出來, 目的就係為佐壓收地價?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T14:38:43.000Z","msg":"//定係拋填海方案出來, 目的就係為佐壓收地價?//<br />\n<br />\n其實要壓價有其他方法<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T14:50:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 問一下. 就棕地地主而言, 渣一塊地放喺度乜都唔理由佢荒廢, 其實有冇成本?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T01:50:49.000Z","msg":"應該無？<br />\n但係好少會就咁擺響度嘅<br />\n一般都係會用作其他用途<br />\n<br />\n事實上係棕地面積係不斷上升緊"},{"pid":"89f24589352e652d36cafd3272ba656011615d15","tid":947772,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-